name: Dinox
overview: Published in November 1993 by Art Project Studios (APS), Musicians: Jeroen Tel, Macmagix & Karl Sommer, Graphicians: Rainer Böhme & Daniel Löwe Programmer: Rainer Böhme, this platformer challenges your reptilian alter ego to find the keys and make your way to the level's exit. You will need to overcome challenges and fiendish traps to do so.
